Install:
	sudo apt install virtualbox

Konfigurasi:
	Download Virtualbox Extension Pack
		https://download.virtualbox.org/virtualbox/5.1.0/

	Install Virtualbox Extension Pack
		preference > ekstension > ...

	Add Your User to vboxusers Group
		$ sudo usermod -aG vboxusers tri
			atau
		$ sudo gpasswd -a yourusername vboxusers
		$ groups yourusername

	Reboot komputer
	Enable USB Controller and Add New USB filter
	Access USB from VirtualBox

Referensi:
	https://www.linuxbabe.com/virtualbox/access-usb-from-virtualbox-guest-os
